stdyInfo.abstract: CAMECA SX100 BSE and SE images, and X-ray element maps from October 2015, December 2015, January 2016, and February 2016.
stdyInfo.notes: All images are labeled with a date. X-ray element maps are labeled with the sample number, sample location, and element. X-ray element maps are provided as original as well as 16 color which was done in imageJ.
